<div class="content-header">Articulations</div>

<div class="content">
    A list of articulations is a type of notation record with discriminator value "articulations".
    Individual articulation records are in the articulation table, joined to the list on field articulations_id.
</div>

<div class="content">
Lined articulations (discriminator values "doit", "falloff", "plop", "scoop" in the articulation table) have their line information in the line table using foreign key line_id.
</div>

